N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 365.1 - Objective

State Regulations

This Part's objective is to establish procedural guidelines
that delineate criteria and which promote consistent probation practices with
respect to the residency of certain sex offenders under probation
supervision. Notes
